OL,3,CBloody Sunday shootings 'unjustified
OL,4,Cand gratuitous', murder trial told
OL,6,FThe family of a man killed on Bloody
OL,7,FSunday has described the start of an
OL,8,FArmy veteran's trial for his murder as
OL,9,Fa "momentous day" in their five-decade
OL,10,Fcampaign for justice.
OL,12,FThe long-awaited trial of the former
OL,13,Fparatrooper accused of two murders in
OL,14,FLondonderry on January 30 1972 began
OL,15,Fat Belfast Crown Court on Monday
OL,16,Fmorning.
