OL,6,FSoldier F, who cannot be identified,
OL,7,Fis accused of murdering James Wray and
OL,8,FWilliam McKinney on a day when members
OL,9,Fof the Parachute Regiment shot dead 13
OL,10,Fcivil rights protesters on the streets
OL,11,Fof Derry.
OL,13,FHe is also charged with five attempted
OL,14,Fmurders during the incident in the
OL,15,Fcity's Bogside area, namely of Joseph
OL,16,FFriel, Michael Quinn, Joe Mahon,
OL,17,FPatrick O'Donnell and a person unknown.
OL,19,FSoldier F has pleaded not guilty to
OL,20,Fthe seven counts.JThe non-jury case is
OL,21,Fbeing heard by judge Patrick Lynch.
