OL,6,F"The defendant was part of a small
OL,7,Fgroup of soldiers who moved west from
OL,8,FRossville Street into that courtyard,"
OL,9,Fhe said. "At the far end civilians,
OL,10,Ffearful of the approach of the
OL,11,Fsoldiers, began running across the
OL,12,Fcourtyard towards a gap at one of the
OL,13,Fcorners in order to escape.
OL,15,F"As they did so, soldiers acting
OL,16,Ftogether, and therefore with joint
OL,17,Fresponsibility, opened fire with their
OL,18,Fself-loading rifles shooting at the
OL,19,Fcivilians as they ran away.
