OL,6,FJohn McKinney, a brother of William
OL,7,FMcKinney, told those gathered: "Today
OL,8,Fmarks a momentous day in our battle to
OL,9,Fsecure justice for our loved ones who
OL,10,Fwere murdered on Bloody Sunday.
OL,12,F"It has taken 53 years to get to this
OL,13,Fpoint, and we have battled all the
OL,14,Fodds to get here.
OL,16,F"Everything that we have achieved to
OL,17,Fthis point has been through relentless
OL,18,Fcommitment and a refusal to lie down.
