OL,6,FThirteen people were killed on the day
OL,7,Fand another man shot by paratroopers
OL,8,Fdied four months later.
OL,10,FMany consider him the 14th victim of
OL,11,FBloody Sunday but his death was
OL,12,Fformally attributed to an inoperable
OL,13,Fbrain tumour.
OL,15,FPolice in Northern Ireland launched a
OL,16,Fmurder investigation after the
OL,17,Flandmark Saville Inquiry, which
OL,18,Freported in 2010, found there was no
OL,19,Fjustification for shooting any of
OL,20,Fthose killed or wounded.
