OL,6,FAt the time of the inquiry's
OL,7,Fpublication, then-prime minister David
OL,8,FCameron issued a public apology,
OL,9,Fsaying the killings were "unjustified
OL,10,Fand unjustifiable".
OL,12,FThe Saville report overturned the long-
OL,13,Fdisputed findings of the 1972 Widgery
OL,14,FTribunal which concluded that the
OL,15,Fsoldiers had been shot at first, and
OL,16,Freturned fire in self-defence.
