OL,6,FThe trial of Soldier A and Soldier C
OL,7,Ffor the 1972 shooting of Official IRA
OL,8,Fleader Joe McCann in Belfast ended in
OL,9,FApril 2021 after a judge ruled that
OL,10,Fkey evidence due to be relied upon by
OL,11,Fthe prosecution was inadmissible.
OL,13,FThe inadmissible evidence was
OL,14,Fstatements given by the soldiers to
OL,15,Fthe Royal Military Police (RMP) in the
OL,16,Faftermath of the shooting.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G17/19
